entries.femaleVariant: Hey, Kirk.
V? Holy shit – barely recognize ya!
See you haven't changed... not a single bit.
entries.maleVariant: I see you haven't changed... not a single bit.

entries.femaleVariant: All right, all right. Listen – job's simple. Got a van standin' not far from here. Brimmin' with merch worth fat digits.
Drivin' to the border tomorrow, but... Lotta things could happen before then, you feel me?
Specifics, Kirk. What's in the van?
Militech implants. Experimental series, shit you can't get on the street. Straight outta some lab in Shanghai.
Nope – I'm out.
All right, I'm in.
You haven't learned a fuckin' thing from that Rayfield fiasco.
Sounds too good to be true... Ergh, fuck it – it's worth a shot at least. Count me in.
Oh, it's true all right. Anyways – send you the coords, see you at the spot. Later!
So come on! Siddown, I'll spill you the detes.
[Sit] All right. Talk.
Start talkin'.
[Stand]
[Stand]
Bye, Kirk. Find another gonk to do your dirty work.
Wait, V! Just think about it! Job's a done deal! Swear on my mother's life!
OK, changed my mind.
Fwoo... OK, changed my mind. Let's do this.
Knew you'd come around! You'll see, V, it's gonna be fuckin' rainin' eddies!
Hey, Kirk. Been a while.
Nice of you to drop by. After our call... Well – thought that was the last I'd hear from ya.
Ha! Well, you know me – I'm ol' fashioned like that. Slow and steady wins the race, huh?
Get to the point.
And who does it belong to?
Jesus, V, who the fuck cares? Once we take it – it's ours! So... can I count on you or not?
Most you could klep is some c-store snacks an' booze. You're a fuckin' joke, Kirk. I only work with people who're serious.
entries.maleVariant: Most you could klep is some c-store snack an' booze. You're a fuckin' joke, Kirk. I only work with people who're serious.

entries.femaleVariant: Let's delta, then. Send you the coords, see you there.
